### Get Twitter Sync Status (Success)
# Returns: { data: { pending: N, archived: N, archives: [...] }, error: null }
# - pending: messages waiting in twitter_imports queue
# - archived: messages archived (failed after max retries or invalid)
# - archives: array of { msg_id, url, failure_reason, archived_at }
GET {{$dotenv API_BASE_URL}}/twitter/sync/status
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv USER_TOKEN}}

### Auth Error - No Token
# Expected: 401 - Not authenticated
GET {{$dotenv API_BASE_URL}}/twitter/sync/status
